Rating: 3
This is a fabulous, quick meal -- a delcious family favorite at my house. I have made it faithfully for years and find it delicious every time. I have made it for company -- always to rave reviews. I am surprised by the reviewers who find the dressing bland -- perhaps the jalepenos available to you are on the mild side and you should up your pepper to a serrano. You can usually smell a jalepeno and know how hot it is going to be. The only thing I do differently to this recipe is toss the cooked, sliced beef in the dressing before adding it to the salad.

